Licensing Restrictions:
The following uses are NOT permitted under this license:

1. **SaaS / Cloud Hosting Restriction**
   You may not use the Licensed Work to provide a hosted, managed, or commercial 
   Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) offering that competes with LoopIQ, FusionOne Inc., 
   or any LoopIQ enterprise or cloud product.

2. **Competitive Service Restriction**
   You may not use the Licensed Work to build any product, platform, or service 
   that is substantially similar to or a replacement for LoopIQ, including but 
   not limited to: SDLC platforms, ITSM systems, test management systems, 
   project management platforms, idea management tools, release governance systems, 
   or AI-driven compliance platforms.

3. **Fork & Rebranding Restriction**
   You may not create a fork, derivative, or modified version of the Licensed Work 
   whose primary purpose is to replace or replicate LoopIQ functionality in the 
   commercial market, or to claim originality of LoopIQ’s design, workflows, 
   architecture, or branding.

4. **Cloud Provider Restriction**
   No cloud provider (including AWS, GCP, Azure, DigitalOcean, Oracle Cloud, etc.) 
   may host, sell, or offer the Licensed Work as part of any commercial or managed 
   service without an explicit, written commercial license from FusionOne Inc.

5. **Trademark Restriction**
   The names “LoopIQ”, “FusionOne”, associated logos, and product branding may
   not be used to advertise or promote derivative works without written permission.

